room_title: Escape room "The Initiative" by Elm City Escape in New Haven
room_description:
It’s your first day of work at OMNE CORP! This is your dream job! Right...? Although you’re excited to begin, you can’t help but feel that something is wrong…
It seems your boss and OMNE might be hiding a secret behind the company's new initiative. Can you find out the truth about your new employer before it’s too late?
